# Armin Lišić — Portfolio

A modern black-and-white web portfolio focused on clean UX, structured layout, and subtle motion design.  
The site presents my projects, workflow, tech stack, and featured work with a calm visual style and clear hierarchy.

Live preview: (add link here)  
Author: https://github.com/Armin-000

---

## Highlights

- minimal black and white visual language  
- smooth micro-interactions and reveal animations  
- orbit hero cards and structured section flow  
- animated decorative background lines  
- responsive layout and clean typography  
- performance-aware effects

The goal of the portfolio is clarity, organization, and professional presentation of work.

---

## Sections

- Hero — intro, orbit animation, scroll hint  
- About — profile, workflow principles, timeline  
- Featured Project — Nexora (local AI assistant)  
- Projects — selected work with GitHub repositories  
- Tech Stack — frontend, backend, tools and workflow  
- Contact — avatar, email link and GitHub button

---

## Technologies

Frontend:

- HTML5  
- CSS (Grid, Flexbox, transitions, animations)  
- JavaScript (ES6)

Other resources:

- Google Fonts  
- Font Awesome Icons

The project is fully static and does not use frameworks or external build tools.

---

## Project Structure

```
/
├─ index.html
├─ css/
